text:

Post to Facebook Vote for our Game of the Week for October 23rd It's time to cast your votes for the Sideline 2015 Game of the Week for Friday, October 23rd.   firstcoastnews.com: http://fcnews.tv/1RLgJAO   Join the Conversation To   Vote for our Game of the Week for October 23rd Chad Cushnir, First Coast News 9:13 p.m. EDT October 15, 2015 Game of the week choices for 10/23/15 (Photo: First Coast News) CONNECT TWEET LINKEDIN COMMENT EMAIL MORE 
It's time to cast your votes for the Sideline 2015 Game of the Week for Friday, October 23rd. 
The matchup with the most votes by the time the poll closes at 11 PM on Wednesday, October 21st will be declared the winner. 
Some of the perks of being the Game of the Week include: Live pre-game reports on First Coast News at 5, 5:30, and 6:00 A live report during the game on First Coast News at 7 Extended coverage of the game during Sideline 2015 on First Coast News at 11 A visit from the First From You Game Box photo booth which will offer the opportunity for free photo strips and the chance to record yourself on a video that could be used on TV during Sideline 2015 
You may vote as many times as you would like in the poll below. If you don't see it on your screen, you can either press the refresh button on your browser or click here for a direct link: http://poll.fm/5focg Read or Share this story: http://fcnews.tv/1RLgJAO TOP VIDEOS
